    "Our water damage service covers every stage of the response. Emergency response (24/7 callout — typically on-site within 2-4 hours for major incidents). Water extraction (submersible pumps for standing water, industrial wet vacuums for soaked carpets and floors, moisture extraction from upholstery and soft furnishings). Drying (professional dehumidifiers — refrigerant and desiccant — air movers, drying chambers for specific areas). Moisture monitoring (moisture meters, thermal imaging cameras — to track drying progress and confirm when materials are dry). Antimicrobial treatment (to prevent mould growth during drying). Deep clean after drying (the property needs a full clean once it's dry — see our Deep House Cleaning service).",
