    "Floor care is a specialist discipline that most general cleaners get wrong. Wrong chemistry on linoleum causes permanent damage (linseed oil substrate is alkaline-sensitive). Wrong pad on marble causes deep scratching (marble is 3 on Mohs scale, softer than the silicon carbide in aggressive pads). Wrong polish on rubber causes permanent discoloration (rubber requires a specific water-based acrylic). Wrong technique on VCT causes 'polish pop' — the layers separate and peel. A floor care mistake is expensive to fix and easy to make. Our floor care specialists are trained on every floor type, every chemistry, every pad — colour-coded systems, chemistry matched to floor type, dust-free stripping where possible, and quarterly inspection programmes.",
    "We handle the full range of commercial and residential hard floors: VCT (vinyl composition tile — the standard commercial floor in schools, hospitals, retail), linoleum (environmentally preferred, alkaline-sensitive), rubber (often in gyms and hospitals, requires water-based acrylic), terrazzo (chip-and-cement, needs diamond polishing), sealed concrete (warehouse and retail, requires densifier and polish), natural stone (marble, granite, slate, limestone — each needs specific protocols). Each floor type has a specific chemistry, specific pad, specific technique. We never use one product across all floors — we tailor the protocol to the floor type, age, condition, and traffic pattern.",
    "Our floor care programmes are built around your traffic pattern and budget. Annual full strip and refinish for high-traffic entrances (the polish takes a beating over 12 months). Quarterly top-up scrub and recoat for medium-traffic zones (extend the life of the polish between full strips). Daily burnish programme for premium floors (polishing pad under a high-speed burner brings back the wet-look gloss every night). Residential natural stone floors — annual diamond-grit restoration (50-grit through 3000-grit) and crystallisation for marble. We work for schools, hospitals, retail chains, hotels, gyms, leisure centres, and premium residential clients across Scotland.",
